The whole point of the post was to say that Osama has won, that the attack on 9/11 had the desired effects. I cannot do anything but agree with it, in fact, this had come to my mind long ago. Worldwide fear has increased, fear about terrorism, saddam, etc. Worldwide, anti-US feelings have increased greatly, both with Afghanistan and now Iraq (although I think in the case of Afghanistan the positive effects outweigh the negative ones - impossible to measure though, the effects of it may really turn up years later).<br>
