<br>
You know, and this comes from the bottom off my heart, I really really hope this dangers don't turn out to be true. I am not anti-war, because I think it is cool and I am not cemented in my opinion. As far as I am concerned you all can go &quot;I told you so&quot; and Iraq becomes a thriving pro-western democracy, which will diminish Muslim extremism in the region. I truely do (yes, seriously).<br>
