I just have no faith in the inspections system, it seems doomed from the start to me.  It was basically designed to observe and document the destruction of those WMD's catalogued at the end of the first gulf war, it was never designed to search out hidden WMD's, and I don't see how it possibly could hope to get ALL of them, or even anything close to all of them.  They don't even have a way of knowing if/when they are done.<br>
<br>
